Screen layout example:

I/ Full screen

When paused, background color should be red

-----------------------------------------------------------
| Menu=Ctrl+T(1) | backup_prog | mode(2) | v0.0.1-??? (3) |
-----------------------------------------------------------
|                                                         |
|                                                         |
|                     DETAILS                             |
|                                                         |
|                                                         |
-----------------------------------------------------------
| 0 warnings 0 erros       | Step ??/???                  |
-----------------------------------------------------------
| tar.gz name           | (4)              | ETA hh:mm:ss | 
-----------------------------------------------------------



1) Or F10
2) Weekly|Complete (len=8)
3) version (len=10+)
4) Elapsed time hh:mm:ss (len=10)


